verbose_text: While EPIT and SLIT induced similar IgG2a levels and also led to a similar reduction in IgE levels in sensitized mice, it was only EPIT that led could significantly reduce eosinophil counts in the bronchoalveolar lavage (BAL) in the asthma model.
